{"id":119843,"date":"2021-03-15T14:25:35","date_gmt":"2021-03-15T14:25:35","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/?p=119843"},"modified":"2021-03-15T14:25:35","modified_gmt":"2021-03-15T14:25:35","slug":"italian-regulator-consob-continues-crackdown-on-scams","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/2021\/03\/15\/italian-regulator-consob-continues-crackdown-on-scams\/","title":{"rendered":"Italian Regulator CONSOB Continues Crackdown on Scams","gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"text"}]},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Italy\u2019s financial regulator &#8211; the Commissione Nazionale per le Societ\u00e0 e la Borsa (CONSOB) has continued its efforts to protect its citizens from unregulated financial companies and possible online scams. The regulator <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.consob.it\/web\/consob-and-its-activities\/news-in-detail\/-\/asset_publisher\/kcxlUuOyjO9x\/content\/press-release-13-3-2021\/718268\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">announced on Friday <\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">that it has blocked several more websites of such firms and is advising all traders to take notice.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The new firms are blocked via the so-called &#8220;Growth Decree&#8221;, on the basis of which Consob can order <\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Internet <\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">connectivity service providers to inhibit access from Italy to the websites through which financial services are offered without due authorization.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Below are the websites Consob has ordered to be blacked out:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211; <\/span><b>KBS Capital Markets Ltd<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> (<\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">website<\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> https:\/\/royaltradefx.com and related page https:\/\/my.royaltradefx.com);<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211; <\/span><b>Donnybrook Consulting Ltd<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> (<\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">website<\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> www.eurofx.trade);<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211; <\/span><b>Investigram Ltd<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> (<\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">website<\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> www.investigram.com);<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211; <\/span><b>FCS Technology Ltd<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> (<\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">website<\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> https:\/\/stockmarketinvest.pro and related page https:\/\/client.stockmarketinvest.pro).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With the addition of these websites, the regulator has indicated that the total number of firms and websites that have been affected this way in Italy is now a total of 400. <\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false,"gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"html"}]},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Italy\u2019s financial regulator &#8211; the Commissione Nazionale per le Societ\u00e0 e la Borsa (CONSOB) has continued its efforts to protect its citizens from unregulated financial companies and possible online scams. The regulator announced on Friday that it has blocked several more websites of such firms and is advising all traders to take notice. &nbsp; The [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false,"gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"html"}]},"author":2,"featured_media":102891,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[54],"tags":[56,57,58,59,60,61,62,63,64,65,66,67,68,71,